            "title": "〈台新新光法說〉觀望中東戰事 投資長：3月起減碼股市 債市保有美元流動性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QRA.ysY2Uay8s4p3f6HckQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/c6c71a5e3bb8ccf60f47da89dde9c61a\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
